    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Fathers and mothers are responsible for the health, the constitution, the development of the character of their children. No one else should be left to see to this work. In becoming the parents of children, it devolves upon you to co-operate with the Lord in educating them in sound principles.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">2<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 126, 1897\" data-link=\"14062.7141001\">Manuscript 126, 1897</span>.</span></a></sup>",
