    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Are not many fathers and mothers placing their responsibilities into others&rsquo; hands? Do not many of them think that the minister should take the burden and see to it that their children are converted and that the seal of God is placed upon them?&rdquo;<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 5-21-1895\" data-link=\"821.14233\">The Review and Herald, May 21, 1895</span>.</span></a></sup>",
